== About ==

r-autoyas is a small ESS complement. It provides automatically created yasnippets for R functions.

Watch the demo screencast: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jLJPorf2LBE (Old version! The key bindings have changed and there are more features now.)

Get source code and more info here: https://github.com/mlf176f2/r-autoyas.el

Requirements:
* yasnippet: http://code.google.com/p/yasnippet/
* Obviously R and ESS
* A R process must be running
* I uploaded the source [[r-autoyas.el|here]].  -- MatthewFidler

